督、强化衔接配合、促进综合治理等作出明确规定。“两高一部”出台意见依法惩治网络暴力违法犯罪-中新网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IoNCy7Lab+fIlEAMaCTEwMDg3NTIzNyDQ6cSoBjAAOBZALHIJNjIzNjgxMjA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-fa9765d9eef5b968f44fb1364ec387fe_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1695654986.53195","card_id":"Q_623679729","target":{"id":623679729,"title":"余承东表示「华为 Mate 60 系列正加班加点紧急生产」，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/623679729","type":"question","created":1695625687,"answer_count":16,"follower_count":37,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1740,5263,21576,44177,105508],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"每经AI快讯，9月25日，华为秋季全场景新品发布会召开。华为常务董事、终端BGCEO、智能汽车解决方案BU董事长余承东发表演讲。余承东表示，华为Mate60系列开启先锋计划以来，广受消费者喜爱，目前正在加班加点紧急生产。余承东：华为Mate60系列目前正在加班加点紧急生产 | 每经网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IoNCy7Lab+fIlEAMaCTEwMDg3NDkxMCDX48SoBjAAOCVALXIJNjIzNjc5NzI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1695654986.54492","card_id":"Q_622155521","target":{"id":622155521,"title":"一万预算穷游十个城市现实吗？吃住行有什么建议吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/622155521","type":"question","created":1694739354,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":69,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[10054,26169,2996912,2996916],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"十个城市分别是西安（二线）.成都（新一线）.桂林（三线）.湛江（三线）.海口（三线）.上饶（三线）.杭州（新一线）.南京（二线）.青岛（新一线）.威海（三线）每个城市分别玩两天，预算一万够吗"},"attached_info":"Cj8IoNCy7Lab+fIlEAMaCTEwMDUzNjM2NSCa146oBjAAOEVALnIJNjIyMTU1NTIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"